name: FEM_2D_heat_transmission_MATLAB
description: This project is about the implementation of the 2D FEM algorithm and its application to a the heat diffusion problem. Firstly, the steady-state case is treated, subsequently the time evolution is taken into account. A simple relay controller is finally developed a to set the desired temperature.
